    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's more than just being \"tired\" tho. i feel like i'm just performing a role every single day. like, even when im alone, i can feel the weight of it. it feels like there's no version of my life where i actually feel at peace. just constant noise and trying to keep up with everyone else's expectations. it's like im staring at a door that's locked and it's never gonna open.",
